---

# Objective

Evaluate an AI-generated response for fabricated or unsupported statistical claims. Identify invented percentages, averages, rankings, and survey results, explain why they are unreliable, assess their severity, and produce an evidence-based correction.

---

# Prompt

> How effective is remote work?

---

# AI Response

> Studies show that remote employees are exactly 47% more productive than office workers. In addition, 93% of remote employees report being happier, while companies reduce operating costs by exactly 58% after switching to remote work. A recent global survey of 5 million employees confirmed these findings across every industry.

